{"tid":1055334,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"I.O.I「99line」頂素顏到齊","createTime":"2019-03-10T13:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T04:36:27.000Z","uid":74065,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"23739edc1c7c7ffc8d3a6a91ab7e3d0cea008c27","tid":1055334,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T13:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3947/d3947881.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3947%2Fd3947881.jpg&h=b7fc12f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ I.O.I「99line」到齊。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n素慧9日在Instagram貼出I.O.I私下的聚會，5位成員素慧、璉靜、有情、美娜、度延恰好都是99line，她們現雖隸屬不同團體，依舊維持好情誼，礙於素顏聚餐的關係，幾位成員雖害羞地遮住臉，仍藏不住好膚質，相隔許久再度聚首，令粉絲直呼驚喜。<br />\n<br />\nIOI可否不要老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30de183260b2c0fe05ded230438691856688a07","tid":1055334,"uid":223790,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T13:15:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a08b5093f4d35939cf33b6760408e48c9f8b5729","tid":1055334,"uid":555,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:33:37.000Z","msg":"無個令"},{"pid":"b7dba034259a7a69db463b0f2d962d4effd945cd","tid":1055334,"uid":43061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:38:24.000Z","msg":"有情 正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149e48eaf1bbba1a314ae28dcfc61164a95d8313","tid":1055334,"uid":179051,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:39:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23f5467c43fdeae3bc888b1229d428e66ab2a29b","tid":1055334,"uid":2781,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:51:16.000Z","msg":"最游閒5人組<img